ssets/36a17b18a2b5497bac8a2368d276d9f9\" width=\"550\" /></p>\n<p>        跨过这道墙的方式有很多，就像那句西方的谚语所说的：All Roads Lead To Rome。VPN 就是其中比较捷径的选择。</p>\n<p>网站地址：<a href=\"http://www.gmailvpn.com/\" title=\"http://www.gmailvpn.com/\">http://www.gmailvpn.com/</a></p>\n<p>VPN介绍：<a href=\"http://louishan.com/articles/free-hideip-vpn.html\" title=\"http://louishan.com/articles/free-hideip-vpn.html\">http://louishan.com/articles/free-hideip-vpn.html</a></p>\n</p>\n<p>  <a href=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/gocomments/xijie.wordpress.com/4731/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/comments/xijie.wordpress.com/4731/\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/godelicious/xijie.wordpress.com/4731/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/delicious/xijie.wordpress.com/4731/\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/gofacebook/xijie.wordpress.com/4731/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/facebook/xijie.wordpress.com/4731/\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/gotwitter/xijie.wordpress.com/4731/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/twitter/xijie.wordpress.com/4731/\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/gostumble/xijie.wordpress.com/4731/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/stumble/xijie.wordpress.com/4731/\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/godigg/xijie.wordpress.com/4731/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/digg/xijie.wordpress.com/4731/\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/goreddit/xijie.wordpress.com/4731/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/reddit/xijie.wordpress.com/4731/\" /></a> <img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://stats.wordpress.com/b.gif?host=xijie.wordpress.com&#038;blog=100680